  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Roast the red bell pepper, carrots, and onion in the oven for 30 minutes, or until tender.",
    "In a large stockpot, combine the roasted vegetables, thyme, ginger, allspice, black pepper, and scotch bonnet pepper.",
    "Deglaze the pot with grapefruit juice, scraping up any browned bits.",
    "Add the coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Strain the broth and discard the solids.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped scotch bonnet pepper if desired."
  ],
